<topic id="xref-no-format-www">
	<title>xref-no-format - WWW link</title>
	<body>
		<p>
			&lt;xref&gt; Any xref referencing a URL should have a format property
		</p>
     <section id="good">
      <title>Good xrefs</title>
			<p><xref format="html" href="http://maps.here.com" scope="external">Sample conformant link http://maps.here.com .</xref></p>
			<p><xref format="html" href="https://maps.here.com:443" scope="external">Sample conformant www link.</xref></p>
    </section>
    <section id="bad">
      <title>Bad xrefs</title>
			<p><xref href="http://maps.here.com" scope="external">Sample non-conformant link http://maps.here.com .</xref></p>
			<p><xref href="https://maps.here.com:443" scope="external">Sample conformant www link.</xref></p>
    </section>
	</body>
</topic>
